title: Frank Sinatra - Greatest Hits, Vol. II
description:
Frank Sinatra - Greatest Hits, Vol. II
(Not to be confused with "Frank Sinatra - Greatest Hits, Vol. 2")



The songs on the original Reprise Stereo LP number K44018 (1032) are:

SIDE ONE

The Shadow Of Your Smile (Live Recording from "Sinatra At The Sands")

Yesterday

Blue Lace

For Once
 
In My Life

Born Free

My Way



SIDE TWO

Little Green Apples

Both Sides, Now

Mrs. Robinson

Call Me Irresponsible

Gentle On My Mind

Love's Been Good To Me
